title: Wide/Extended compliment to Garage Gothic?
content:
Hi all,  
 I'm looking for a wider compliment to Garage Gothic.  
What I have in mind would be something to the effect of [these old Blue Note Miles Davis covers.](http://web.archive.org/web/20131020234141/http:/www.gokudo.co.jp/Record/BlueNote2/index.htm) (the first two on the page)

Thanks in advance,

jr
author: Doc Friendly
